trans-unit.source: Represents the style properties for an element of a control that renders as a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer stilegenskaper for et element i en kontroll som gjengir som en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The TableItemStyle class represents the style properties for an element of a control that renders as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TableItemStyle representerer stilegenskaper for et element i en kontroll som gjengir som <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableRow>

trans-unit.source: You can control the vertical and horizontal alignment of the contents in an item of the table by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.HorizontalAlign%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.VerticalAlign%2A> properties, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Du kan kontrollere loddrette og vannrette justering av innholdet i et element i tabellen ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.HorizontalAlign%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.VerticalAlign%2A>Egenskaper henholdsvis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.VerticalAlign%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.HorizontalAlign%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also specify whether the contents of the cell automatically continue on the next line when the end of the cell is reached by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.Wrap%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også angi om innholdet i cellen fortsetter automatisk på den neste linjen når slutten av cellen nås ved å angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.Wrap%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.Wrap%2A>

trans-unit.source: This class provides methods that are useful for creating a style for an item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table> control.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen inneholder metoder som er nyttige for å opprette en stil for et element i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Table>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.CopyFrom%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.MergeWith%2A> methods to copy or merge the style properties of another TableItemStyle with the instance of the TableItemStyle that the method is called from.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.CopyFrom%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.MergeWith%2A>metoder for å kopiere eller flette stilegenskaper av en annen TableItemStyle med forekomsten av TableItemStyle metoden kalles fra.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.MergeWith%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.CopyFrom%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"></xref> class using default values.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"> </xref> klasse bruker standardverdiene.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"></xref> class with the specified state bag.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"> </xref> klassen med den angitte tilstanden-samling.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class using the specified <xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen ved hjelp av den angitte <xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateBag?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateBag"></xref> that represents the state bag in which to store style information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.StateBag"> </xref> som representerer tilstand egenskapssamling der du vil lagre stilinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: Adds information about horizontal alignment, vertical alignment, and wrap to the list of attributes to render.
trans-unit.target: Legger til informasjon om vannrett justering, loddrett justering og tekstbryting i listen over attributter til å gjengi.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.AddAttributesToRender%2A> method is used primarily by control developers to insert additional attributes and styles in the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> output stream for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.AddAttributesToRender%2A>Metoden brukes hovedsakelig av kontrollutviklere å sette inn flere attributter og stiler i <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter>output-dataflyten for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriter> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.AddAttributesToRender%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.AddAttributesToRender%2A> method overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.AddAttributesToRender%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.AddAttributesToRender%2A>metoden overstyring av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.AddAttributesToRender%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style.AddAttributesToRender%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle.AddAttributesToRender%2A>

trans-unit.source: The output stream that renders HTML content to the client.
trans-unit.target: Output-dataflyten som gjengir HTML-innhold til klienten.

trans-unit.source: The control that the style refers to.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen som stilen refererer til.

trans-unit.source: Duplicates the non-empty style properties of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> into the instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"></xref> class that this method is called from.
trans-unit.target: Dupliserer egenskapene ikke-tomme stilen for den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> i forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"> </xref> klassen som denne metoden kalles fra.

trans-unit.source: Use the CopyFrom method to duplicate the non-empty style properties of the specified <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> into the instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class that this method is called from.
trans-unit.target: Bruk metoden CopyFrom duplisere de ikke-tomme stilegenskaper for det angitte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>i forekomsten av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen som denne metoden kalles fra.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > All properties in the current instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class are replaced by the associated property in the `s` parameter.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Alle egenskapene i den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen er erstattet med den tilknyttede egenskapen i den `s` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> that represents the style to copy.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> som representerer stilen for å kopiere.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the horizontal alignment of the contents in a cell.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir vannrett justering av innholdet i en celle.

trans-unit.source: Use the HorizontalAlign property to specify the horizontal alignment of the data list control within its container.
trans-unit.target: Bruk HorizontalAlign-egenskapen til å angi vannrett justering av kontrollen for dataene i beholderen.

trans-unit.source: This property is set with one of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er angitt med en av de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>nummereringsverdier.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the possible values.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser mulige verdier.

trans-unit.source: |Value|Description| |-----------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The horizontal alignment is not set.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The contents of a cell are left justified within the cell.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Alignment>|The contents of a cell are centered within the cell.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>|The contents of a cell are right justified within the cell.| The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: | Verdien | Beskrivelse | |-----------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>| Vannrett justering er ikke angitt. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>| Innholdet i en celle er venstrejustert i cellen. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Alignment>| Innholdet i en celle er midt i cellen. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>| Innholdet i en celle er høyrejustert i cellen. | Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign> </xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.Alignment> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign"></xref> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign"> </xref> nummereringsverdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_NotSet" name="NotSet" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_NotSet" name="NotSet" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The specified horizontal alignment is not one of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign"></xref> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte vannrett justeringen er ikke én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HorizontalAlign"> </xref> nummereringsverdier.

trans-unit.source: Combines the style properties of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> into the instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"></xref> class that this method is called from.
trans-unit.target: Kombinerer stilegenskaper for det angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> i forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle"> </xref> klassen som denne metoden kalles fra.

trans-unit.source: Use the MergeWith method to combine the style properties of the specified <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> into the instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class that this method is called from.
trans-unit.target: Bruk metoden MergeWith for å kombinere stilegenskaper for det angitte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>i forekomsten av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen som denne metoden kalles fra.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: This method joins the properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> object and the current instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden slår egenskaper på <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objektet og den gjeldende forekomsten av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: This is accomplished by setting each property that is not set in the current instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class with the value in the corresponding property of the `s` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjøres ved å angi hver egenskap som ikke er angitt i den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen med verdien i den tilsvarende egenskapen for den `s` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: Only properties that have not been set are replaced.
trans-unit.target: Bare egenskaper som ikke er angitt erstattes.

trans-unit.source: If a property in the `s` parameter is not set, it does not replace the corresponding property in the current instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en egenskap i den `s` parameteren er ikke angitt, erstatter ikke den tilsvarende egenskapen i den gjeldende forekomsten av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> that represents the style to combine.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> som representerer stilen til å kombinere.

trans-unit.source: Removes any defined style elements from the style.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner alle definerte malen elementer fra stilen.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to remove any defined style elements from the style, leaving the style in its default configuration.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å fjerne noen definerte malen elementer fra stilen avslutter stilen i standardkonfigurasjonen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the vertical alignment of the contents in a cell.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den loddrette justeringen av innholdet i en celle.

trans-unit.source: Use the VerticalAlign property to specify the vertical alignment of the contents of the cell.
trans-unit.target: Bruk VerticalAlign-egenskapen til å angi den loddrette justeringen av innholdet i cellen.

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the possible values.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser mulige verdier.

trans-unit.source: |Vertical Alignment|Description| |------------------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>|The vertical alignment is not set.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>|The contents of the cell are aligned with the upper edge of the cell.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>|The contents of the cell are aligned with the center of the cell.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>|The contents of the cell are aligned with the lower edge of the cell.| The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: | Loddrett justering | Beskrivelse | |------------------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>| Den loddrette justeringen er ikke angitt. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>| Innholdet i cellen er justert etter den øvre kanten av cellen. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>| Innholdet i cellen er justert med midten av cellen. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>| Innholdet i cellen er justert etter den nedre kanten av cellen. | Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign"></xref> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign"> </xref> nummereringsverdier.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_NotSet" name="NotSet" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_NotSet" name="NotSet" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The specified vertical alignment was not one of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign"></xref> enumeration values.
trans-unit.target: Den angitte loddrette justeringen er ikke en av de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.VerticalAlign"> </xref> nummereringsverdier.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the contents of a cell wrap in the cell.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om innholdet i en celle brytes i cellen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Wrap property to specify or determine whether the contents of the cell wrap.
trans-unit.target: Bruk brytes-egenskapen til å angi eller fastslå om innholdet i cellen brytes.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property is stored in view state.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for denne egenskapen lagres i visningsstatusen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the contents of the cell wrap in the cell; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis innholdet i cellen bryte i cellen. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.
